What is KezaKhiq

The name is derived from the two Zulu words "Buyekeza" & "Umkhiqizo" meaning Product Review 

Which sums up the true purpose of KezaKhiq in reviewing products on the South African market as well as bringing much needed attention to new & alternative products.
